<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Zero Hunger NGO</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            background-color: #f4f4f4;
        }

        main {
            max-width: 800px;
            margin: 40px auto;
            padding: 20px;
            background-color: #fff;
            box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }

        h1 {
            color: #333;
        }

        p {
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #555;
        }

        a {
            text-decoration: none;
            color: #007bff;
        }

        .btn {
            display: inline-block;
            padding: 8px 16px;
            font-size: 16px;
            font-weight: bold;
            text-align: center;
            text-decoration: none;
            background-color: #007bff;
            color: #fff;
            border-radius: 4px;
            transition: background-color 0.3s ease;
        }

            .btn:hover {
                background-color: #0056b3;
            }

        .row {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
        }

        .col-md-4 {
            flex: 0 0 32%;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }

            .col-md-4:last-child {
                margin-right: 0; /* Remove right margin for the last column */
            }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

    <main>
        <section class="row" aria-labelledby="aspnetTitle">
            <h1 id="title">Zero Hunger NGO</h1>
            <p class="lead">We work to feed deprived people and children by utilizing excess food from events, offices, and buffets in Dhaka city.</p>
            <p><a href="#" class="btn btn-primary btn-md">Learn more &raquo;</a></p>
        </section>

        <div class="row">
            <section class="col-md-4" aria-labelledby="gettingStartedTitle">
                <h2 id="gettingStartedTitle">Getting started</h2>
                <p>Join us in our mission to make use of excess food and feed those in need.</p>
                <p><a class="btn btn-outline-dark" href="#">Learn more &raquo;</a></p>
            </section>
            <section class="col-md-4" aria-labelledby="librariesTitle">
                <h2 id="librariesTitle">Our Mission</h2>
                <p>We collaborate with restaurants to collect excess food before it gets wasted. Help us make a difference.</p>
                <p><a class="btn btn-outline-dark" href="#">Learn more &raquo;</a></p>
            </section>
            <section class="col-md-4" aria-labelledby="hostingTitle">
                <h2 id="hostingTitle">Get Involved</h2>
                <p>Be a part of our team. We are always looking for volunteers to help us collect and distribute food.</p>
                <p><a class="btn btn-outline-dark" href="#">Learn more &raquo;</a></p>
            </section>
        </div>
    </main>

</body>
</html>
